Sean 
\begin_inset Formula $a:=\sum_{i\in I}a_{i}\alpha_{1}^{i_{1}}\cdots\alpha_{p}^{i_{p}},b:=\sum_{j\in J}b_{i}\beta_{1}^{j_{1}}\cdots\beta_{q}^{i_{q}}\in K(S)$
